<p style="text-align: left;">美股周五大幅反 <span>弹</span>之 <span>际</span>，航空股成 <span>为</span>除了科技股之外表 <span>现</span>最好的板 <span>块</span>之一。 </p>
<p><span>当地时间</span><span>9</span><span>月</span><span>25</span><span>日，在波音的带领下，</span>美股航空 <span>股集体上涨，</span>波音 <span>涨</span><span>6.85%</span><span>，</span>美国航空 <span>涨</span><span>4.42%</span><span>，</span>达美航空 <span>涨</span><span>2.65%</span><span>，</span>西南航空 <span>涨</span><span>0.65%</span><span>，</span><span>联合航</span>空 <span>涨</span><span>4.46%</span><span>。</span></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
